\begin{question}
Please write a short essay (about 100-150 words) on the following topic: The importance of having a mentor in one's career.
\end{question}

\begin{solution}
Having a mentor in one's career is crucial for professional growth and success. A mentor provides guidance, support, and valuable insights, helping to navigate the complexities of the workplace. They offer constructive feedback, which enables individuals to improve their skills

